{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_12_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 ちょっと意識していた人",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "佐伯遙子、じゅうほにゃ歳でっす！\n……ダメね。これじゃ、なんだか噛んじゃったみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko Saeki‚ sheventeen years old!\n…No good. That kind of sounded like I stumbled over my words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "普段ならファンも私も気にしないけど、今回だけは……\n『十七歳でっす！』なんて、とても言えないわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally neither the fans nor I would mind‚ but this time…\nI really can’t bring myself to say‚ “I’m 17 years old!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3292517026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（スタジオから声が聞こえるが……今日は練習）\n（予定のアイドルはいなかったはず。自主練かな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can hear voices from the studio… but there shouldn’t have been）\n（any idols scheduled to practice today. Maybe it’s self-practice?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 35.6924262683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "佐伯遙子でっす、はるぴって呼んでね！\nバイブス爆アゲでいっくよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko Saeki—call me Harupi!\nLet’s crank the vibes way up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "む、無理っ！　バイブスってそもそもどういう意味？\n爆アゲ、はなんとなく分かるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no way! What does “vibes” even mean in the first place?\nI kind of get “cranking it up‚” but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3131745656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、表面だけ若い子をなぞってもダメね\nはぁ～～……って、そんなに歳は離れてないわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ just copying what younger kids do on the surface won’t work.\nHaaah… hey‚ it’s not like I’m that much older!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1841971988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……俺は……何を目撃してしまったんだ？）\n（……見なかったことにしよう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…What… did I just witness?）\n（…I’ll pretend I didn’t see anything.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あれっ、{user}君……！？\nもしかして、今、見てた？　……見たわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ {user}-kun…!?\nYou didn’t just see that‚ did you? …You did‚ didn’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4630836804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "は、遙子さん？　俺は何も……何も見てません\n……誰にも言いませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Haruko-san? I didn’t see anything… nothing at all.\n…I won’t tell anyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それは見たってことじゃない！\nちょっと、こっちでじっくりお話、しよっか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That means you did see it!\nHey‚ how about we talk things through over here for a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8918140728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6071861264
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6071861264
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、さっきは衣装を着てなんの練習を\nしていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what kind of practice were you doing earlier\nwhile wearing that costume?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、さっきからなんで目を合わせてくれないの？\n……私がちょっとヘンテコな行動をしてたのは認めるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ why won’t you look me in the eye?\n…I admit I was acting a little weird.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0683447519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.377843634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "その……ちょっとね、試行錯誤していたのよ\nほら、今度バレンタインのお仕事があるじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was‚ um… just doing some trial and error.\nYou know‚ we’ve got that Valentine’s job coming up‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2350114185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.4489324567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "サニピが出演するバレンタイン関連の仕事ですね\nさっきの衣装はそれで着る物ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Valentine-related work Sunny Peace is appearing in‚ right?\nThat outfit earlier is for that‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.5590685842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、知ってると思うけどこの衣装を着て\nバレンタインチョコのCMを撮影したり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. As you probably know‚ wearing this outfit‚\nwe’ll shoot a Valentine chocolate CM‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1784808794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "チョコを買った人が応募出来るバレンタイン当日の\nファンイベントに出演したりするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and appear at a Valentine’s Day fan event\nthat people who bought the chocolate can apply to attend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7995306428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.6733767507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それが、さっきの練習とどんな関係があるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And how does that relate to the practice you were doing earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6733767507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.2971635499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇとね……その……制服、に問題があるっていうか\n……恥ず……っていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ um… it’s just… the uniform is kind of an issue…\n…It’s embarra— I mean…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1689343452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　すみません、もう少し大きな声でお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Sorry‚ could you speak up a little?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1495902377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.1495902377
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.1707464216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　衣装よ、衣装！　あの衣装！\n現役高校生の隣で私が制服みたいな衣装を着るのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh! I mean the costume! That costume!\nI’ll be wearing a uniform-like outfit next to actual high school students‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.0900905291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.7300890284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "ものすごーーく、気まずいの！\n五人の中で私だけが、制服を卒業しちゃってるのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s reeeally awkward!\nI’m the only one of the five who’s already graduated from wearing uniforms!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.2900905291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃね、アイドルだもん\n必要ならどんな衣装だって着るわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ I’m an idol‚\nso I’ll wear any outfit if it’s necessary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.1567571957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 202.1548960047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "でもね、現役高校生と、あの制服みたいな衣装で並ぶの\n私には凄く、すごーく……大問題なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But standing next to current high schoolers in that uniform-like outfit\nis a really‚ reeeally… big problem for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.3567571957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったんですか……俺にはよく分かりませんが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… I can’t really relate‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.2296944616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 219.7764063833
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "私、星見プロに入る前、アイドルになりたくて\nオーディションを受けまくってた時期があってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before I joined Hoshimi Pro‚ I really wanted to be an idol‚\nso there was a time when I went to auditions nonstop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.4701266288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "その時、初々しさがない、みたいな評価も受けたのよ\n当時中学生だったんだけど……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I even got comments like “you lack freshness.”\nI mean‚ I was in middle school back then… haha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.4701266288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 238.9142296154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "大体、制服は卒業しちゃった年齢なのよ\n痛いとか、似合わないとか、笑われたりしないかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m basically past the age of wearing uniforms.\nWhat if people think it’s cringe‚ or that it doesn’t suit me‚ and laugh…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.3367932955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 250.1992409388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと、絶対にありません\n制服姿、とてもよく似合ってますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That won’t happen. Absolutely not.\nYou look great in a uniform.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.033324178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう？　でも……二十代で、十代の子とお揃いの\n制服っぽい衣装で並んだら、やっぱり……浮いちゃうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really? But… being in my twenties‚ if I wore a uniform-style outfit\nmatching teenagers‚ I’d still look out of place… wouldn’t I…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.9089249927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 269.866932233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "浮いたりなんてしませんよ。本当にお似合いです\n佐伯遙子、十七歳、制服だって現役でいけますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wouldn’t look out of place at all. It truly suits you.\nHaruko Saeki‚ 17 years old—uniforms still work just fine for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.7666432698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に？　……じゃあ、今回もこれからも\n佐伯遙子十七歳をもっと打ち出していこうかな～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Really? …Then maybe this time‚ and from now on too‚\nI’ll push “Saeki Haruko‚ 17 years old” even more~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.2987250644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 290.1345060348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね。そうなると、事務所としては\n星見高校に再入学の手続きを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good. In that case‚ as an agency‚\nI’ll arrange your re-enrollment at Hoshimi high school…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.3999766032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 297.7733040491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
