      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}君\nちょっと面白がってるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-kun.\nYou’re having a bit too much fun‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.9375230787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、元気を取り戻してもらおうと思って\nふざけ過ぎました……でも、少しは元気が出ましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry—I just wanted to cheer you up.\nI went too far… but did it help even a little?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 305.2333099365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 310.4491995493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
