      "text": "最後のはやり過ぎよ！　……っふふ\nもう、気心が知れてるのも考えものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That last one was too much! …Fufu.\nHonestly… being this close has its drawbacks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.8726256283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
