      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "ありがと。これだけ似合うって言ってもらえたんだもん\n今のままの私で、頑張ってみる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. If you say it suits me this much‚\nI’ll try my best as I am now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 323.0771373747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
