      "text": "制服かぁ……サニピで恋愛ソングを作るのは\nこれが初めてだけど、私って、恋愛経験ないのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A uniform‚ huh… This is the first time Sunny Peace\nis making a love song‚ but I don’t really have romantic experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 331.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "中学生の頃からアイドルの練習生をやったし\nそれまでだって、ずっとアイドルを目指していたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been an idol trainee since middle school‚\nand even before that‚ I was always aiming to be an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.8438040414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 345.9294487636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛をするような、気持ちの余裕なんてなかった\n……ううん、アイドルの道以外、何も見えてなかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never had the emotional space for romance.\n…No‚ I couldn’t see anything but the path of being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.3878056615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_12_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "悪いことじゃありませんよ。それだけアイドルに\n強い想いを抱いていたってことでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not a bad thing. It just means\nyou cared that deeply about being an idol‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 359.2333099365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 362.2899932544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
