      "text": "そうかも。だからバレンタインも全然ピンとこなくて\nあ、そういえば一個だけバレンタインの思い出、あるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe. That’s why Valentine’s Day never really clicked for me.\nOh—actually‚ I do have one Valentine’s memory.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.4263435679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
