      "text": "バレンタインの思い出……？\nそれは初耳です。教えてもらってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A Valentine’s memory…?\nThat’s the first I’ve heard of it. Would you tell me about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
